Timothy Nutter is a teacher, dancer, choreographer and musician who lives and works in Davis. He is artistic director of the Art Theater of Davis, a community theater group dedicated to staging modern classics. Timothy also works as a writing tutor (for more information, see The Choice of Words). For information about Timothys dance teaching, check out TimothyNutterDance Classical and Contemporary Dance Classes with Timothy Nutter. Timothy no longer hosts the Monticello Open Mic, as it has been discontinued.



